#000001 [workaround]

Errormessage:
../../src/xcb_io.c:183: process_responses: Assertion `!(req && current_request && !(((long) (req->sequence) - (long) (current_request)) <= 0))' failed.

Trigger:
Occurs when resizing the window while rendering.

Possible source of bug:
tgTomGineThread

System:
Ubuntu 10.04
Kernel Linux 2.6.32-33-generic
OpenGL Version: 3.2.0 NVIDIA 195.36.24

Links:
https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=616640

Workaround:
Be sure you haven't switched Visual Effects to None.
System -> Preferences -> Visual Effects

